00:01:15.620 --> 00:01:18.140
sort of infirmity.

00:01:18.140 --> 00:01:20.780
This was Jesus' third tour of Galilee.

00:01:20.780 --> 00:01:23.819
He was teaching, preaching, and curing.

00:01:23.819 --> 00:01:26.980
What effect did it have on him, verse 36?

00:01:26.980 --> 00:01:31.760
