00:01:31.760 --> 00:01:34.700
about like sheep without a shepherd.

00:01:34.700 --> 00:01:41.620
The footnote tells us that the verb here for pity denotes a feeling experienced deep inside

00:01:41.620 --> 00:01:50.019
the body, an intense emotion, one of the strongest words in Greek for compassion.

00:01:50.019 --> 00:01:55.620
